---
import { GithubIcon, EmailIcon, LinkedInIcon } from '@/components/icons';
---

<section class="mb-10 flex items-center gap-5 border-b border-line pb-10">
  <img
    src="/img/main/img_profile.png"
    alt="삔야 프로필"
    class="size-20 shrink-0 rounded-full object-cover sm:size-24"
    loading="eager"
  />
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink sm:text-2xl">삔야</h2>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <a href="https://github.com/bbinya1224" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="GitHub" class="text-subtle transition-colors hover:text-ink">
          <GithubIcon />
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:bbinya1224@gmail.com" aria-label="Email" class="text-subtle transition-colors hover:text-ink">
          <EmailIcon />
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bbinya" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="LinkedIn" class="text-subtle transition-colors hover:text-ink">
          <LinkedInIcon />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-subtle break-keep sm:text-base">
      코드와 커뮤니케이션을 함께 설계하려고 노력하는 프론트엔드 개발자입니다.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
